instruction: Make a list of the main actors in The Lord of the Rings.
output:
1. Elijah Wood as Frodo Baggins 
2. Ian McKellen as Gandalf 
3. Orlando Bloom as Legolas 
4. Sean Astin as Samwise Gamgee 
5. Viggo Mortensen as Aragorn 
6. Liv Tyler as Arwen 
7. Cate Blanchett as Galadriel 
8. John Rhys-Davies as Gimli 
9. Christopher Lee as Saruman 
10. Hugo Weaving as Elrond 
11. Andy Serkis as Gollum
